nodes.text: Nagratha served as the Supreme Chancellor of the Galactic Republic circa 7786 BBY. During the Waymancy Storm conflict of 7811 BBY, Nagratha's mother had served with the Squill Sifters intercepting and decoding Waymancy communications. The Chancellor attended the 25th anniversary of victory in the Waymancy Storm and delivered a commemorative speech for the occasion.
